{"tid":917061,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔明女仔,也不明拍拖結婚,更不懂戀愛。","createTime":"2018-11-26T06:38:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T09:37:13.000Z","uid":140357,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"593cac0c111e6472f136579edde307cfd026523b","tid":917061,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:38:55.000Z","msg":"拍拖忘記時間,忘記了到底要拍幾耐。<br />\n<br />\n結婚,本身就是承諾一生。拍拖就是打下結婚基礎,但耐了還沒有基礎,有些事就要明。<br />\n<br />\n所以女仔話人chur,我唔明,難道要我拖你青春10年8年?感覺對了,就試着交往,交往好了,就承諾一生,難道我錯了?"},{"pid":"6957df3d656207eb7ef1bb924d69c7744fd13a12","tid":917061,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:41:49.000Z","msg":"我想做你嘅專屬小丑,唔係一個好人小丑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3a31ec1b6711bf810777101890876b4db9c8dd","tid":917061,"uid":10544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:42:24.000Z","msg":"唯有摺埋一舊啦"},{"pid":"52ddee80a461247127d12785bc912bf905715786","tid":917061,"uid":97364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:48:29.000Z","msg":"見你又呻，係求婚失敗?? 拍左幾耐??"},{"pid":"308dc96964f335b7f21b8dfe4daf61e7079acf48","tid":917061,"uid":164167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T08:06:29.000Z","msg":"係麵包！"},{"pid":"dfa727b1759463070ba929633512132fd46469aa","tid":917061,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"308dc96964f335b7f21b8dfe4daf61e7079acf48","tid":917061,"uid":164167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T08:06:29.000Z","msg":"係麵包！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:33:34.000Z","msg":"日本麵包61號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52fd3d51865fcf070cfcc6629171a969372ce314","tid":917061,"uid":164167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfa727b1759463070ba929633512